<A>__{a nurse applies sencors to the head, breast, arms, and fingers of nancy thompson. the girl is lying on a simple broad cot, in her pajamas. the room is subdued in color and holds only this single bed. a large mirror set into one wall hides an observation room beyond.}
<C>__{nancy}
<D>__{but i just don't feel... ready to sleep yet. please, do i have to?}
<A>__{wider, revealing dr samuel king, a young, curly haired internist; intelligent and wry. he treats nancy at all times like a young adult, never patronizing. he winks as the nurse finishes.}
<C>__{dr king}
<D>__{don't worry, you're not gonna change into bride of frankenstein or anything.}
<A>__{nancy manages a smile, but she's haggard and visibly thinner. marge, background, looks downright distraught.}
