<D>__{please, nancy. trust us.}
<A>__{the girls gauges her mother, the doctor, the situation very carefully. then lowers her eyes.}
<C>__{nancy}
<D>__{it's not you i don't trust. it's...}
<P>__{(gives up)}
<D>__{okay. let's do it.}
<A>__{greatly relieved, marge gives nancy a goodnight kiss, then follows the doctor through a doorway near the mirror. as soon as her mother is out of sight, nancy's eyes drift to the mirror itself. in its reflection she sees herself looking back, alone on the bed.}
